nts><div class=headingArea><div id=heading>TSP:&nbsp<br>TSP Name:&nbsp<br>Critical Notice Description:&nbsp<br>Notice Effective Date:&nbsp<br>Notice Effective Time:&nbsp<br>Notice End Date:&nbsp<br>Notice End Time:&nbsp<br>Notice Identifier:&nbsp<br>Notice Status Description:&nbsp<br>Notice Type:&nbsp<br>Posting Date:&nbsp<br>Posting Time:&nbsp<br>Prior Notice Identifier:&nbsp<br>Required Response<br>&nbsp; Indicator Description:&nbsp<br>Response Date:&nbsp<br>Response Time:&nbsp<br>Subject:&nbsp<br></div><div id=headingData>007921323<br>East Tennessee Natural Gas, LLC<br>Critical notice<br>02/07/2026<br>09:00:00 AM<br>02/08/2026<br>09:00:00 AM<br>173599<br>Initiate<br>Operational Flow Order<br>02/05/2026<br>03:00:00 PM<br> <br><br>No response required<br> <br> <br>ETNG Operational Flow Order -- EFF 2/7<br></div></div><br><div id=bulletin><br><div id=heading>Notice Text:</div><br><p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\\\"><a><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">In order to maintain the operational integrity of the system, ETNG is issuing a Balancing Alert Operational Flow Order (OFO) pursuant to Section 14.7 of the General Terms and Conditions of ETNG's FERC Gas Tariff effective 9:00 AM CCT, February 7, 2026 for </span></span></a><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">all </span></span></span><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">LMSMA and LMSPA parties</span></span></span><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">.</span></span></span><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\"><br> <br> This OFO does not affect the ability of ETNG to receive or deliver quantities of gas for scheduled nominations to any customer, storage field, or pipeline.<br> <br> During the effectiveness of this OFO, balancing parties under Rate Schedules LMSMA and LMSPA must be balanced such that actual deliveries of gas out of the system must be equal to or less than scheduled deliveries out of the system and actual receipts of gas into the system must be equal to or greater than scheduled receipts into the system.</span></span></span></p> \\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\\\"><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\"><br> The penalty provisions under Section 47.5(b) of the General Terms and Conditions of ETNG's FERC Gas Tariff shall apply for failure to conform for each dekatherm of actual receipt quantities that are less than scheduled receipt quantities and for each dekatherm of actual delivery quantities that are greater than scheduled delivery quantities, in each case with a tolerance of 10% of scheduled quantities or 500 dekatherms (whichever is greater).<br> <br> In addition, ETNG will not permit retroactive nominations to avoid an OFO penalty except for shippers who can secure day ending Due Shipper supply.</span></span></span></p> \\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 13px; line-height: 115%; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\\\"><span><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\"><br> This OFO will remain in effect until 9:00 AM CCT, February 8, 2026.<br> <br> <span style=\\\"color: black;\\\">Please contact your Operations Account Representative should you have any questions.</span></span></span></span></p> \\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 13px; line-height: 115%; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\\\"><span><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">Please refer to the table below for the effected ETNG operational areas, dates, and tolerance percentages.</span></span></p> \\n<table border=\\\"1\\\" width=\\\"626\\\" style=\\\"width: 624px; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\\\"> \\n <tbody> \\n  <tr> \\n   <td width=\\\"138\\\" valign=\\\"top\\\" style=\\\"width: 138px; border: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0in 7px;\\\"> <p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\\\"><span><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">Operational Areas</span></b></span></p> </td> \\n   <td width=\\\"125\\\" style=\\\"width: 125px; border-top: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0in;\\\"> <p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center;\\\"><span><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: black;\\\">Gas Day </span></b></span></p> <p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center;\\\"><span><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">Feb 5</span></b></span></p> </td> \\n   <td width=\\\"126\\\" style=\\\"width: 125px; border-top: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0in 7px;\\\"> <p style=\\\"margin: 0in; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center;\\\"><span><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\\\">Gas Day Feb 6</span></b></span></p> </td> \\n   <td width=\\\"109\\\" style=\\\"width: 109px; border-top: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0in;\\\"> <p style=\\\"margin: 0